# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository; Git checks out native line
# endings per platform. Kills the "LF will be replaced by CRLF" churn on Windows
# and makes diffs deterministic across contributors. Overrides core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize, never touch bytes. (SVG/XML are text and are
# intentionally left to the rule above.)
*.webm binary
*.mp4 binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
